subject: Baseball
lead_paragraph: In April, Robinson Cano, Jayson Nix, Kevin Youkilis and Lyle Overbay caught the visiting Orioles in a rare 4-6-5-6-5-3-4 triple play, a memorable moment in an otherwise disappointing season.
